例： Cigarette smoking used to be more common among affluent people. 吸烟过去在富人中更为普遍。 

2. N-PLURAL The affluent are people who are affluent. 富人 

例： The diet of the affluent has not changed much over the decades. 富人的饮食数十年来没怎么变。

